== Introduction ==

A simple mode that currenly only gives syntax highlighting to file synchronization progam [http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/unison/ unison's] configuration files. Source is available at [https://github.com/impaktor/unison-mode github].

== Install ==
Download the source code to your load-path, and put the following in your configuration file:
{{{
(autoload 'unison-mode "unison-mode" "my unison mode" t)
(setq auto-mode-alist (append '(("\\.prf$" . unison-mode)) auto-mode-alist))
}}}
